sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as ServiceList
    participant Manager as ServiceManager
    participant Loader as ServiceTemplateLoader

    User->>CLI: service:list
    alt available mode
        CLI->>Loader: loadAll templates
        Loader-->>CLI: templates
        CLI-->>User: grouped template list
    else configured mode
        CLI->>Manager: getServices
        CLI->>Manager: getEnabled
        Manager-->>CLI: services and enabled
        CLI-->>User: service status list
    end
